  went wrong for 16bit charsets. (tstich)
- Synchronize Subsribed missed some deleted folders. Adjusted the traversing 
  index when a child got removed from the list. (tstich)
- Added more information on the messageFlagedChanged event. With this 
  additional information it is now possible to update the VFolders 
  correctly if the flags change. Further a new search is triggered 
  if the flags change so that the VFolders get these changes. There 
  is still a good way missing for removing messages after a Flag change. (tstich)
