  add more options in the future, a plugin selection dialog, currently
  supports filtering/sorting/threadedview/columns configuration (fdietz)
- visible columns can be customized with new dialog, see 
  View->Configure Columns.. menuitem (fdietz)
- added Message coloring support, added filter and filter action (redsolo)
- cleanup of all addressbook dialogs (fdietz)
- added tooltips to message-list columns (fdietz)
- fixed exception dialog layout (fdietz)
- SMTP/IMAP/POP3 authentication cleanups, includes automatically selecting the
  most secure method, including updates in the account dialog, to query
  for these methods (tstich)
- filters can be enabled/disabled (fdietz)
- cleanup of filter framework (fdietz)
- cleanup of JTree folder DND, added DND of messages support (redsolo)
- added subscribe dialog (tstich)
- replaced log4j, with java.util.logging (javaprog)
- cleanup of composer.commands, using inputstreams only (tstich)
- added account-based filter (redsolo)
- new About Dialog, added contributors list, added memory monitor (ryad kalla/javaprog)
- cleanup of the action infrastructure (javaprog)
- cleanup of message-builder package (fdietz)
- added spam column, spam filters, filter actions, mark as spam/not spam actions (fdietz)
- refactored Config framework (javaprog)
- refactored startup process and session management (javaprog)
- improved mnemonic handling in resource loading framework
- improved reaction to deleted messages by other applications (e.g. virus killers) while columba is running.
- added "Open Link/With" items to message-viewer context-menu

Fixed bugs:
- fixed error in printing when no character set is specified
  in message (karlpeder)
- the correct account is now selected when replying (karlpeder)
- fixed bug which caused attachments to be dupplicated when 
  switching between html and plain text in the composer (karlpeder)
